<textList name="BS_AUTO_SUICIDE_SUCCESS_TEXT">
	<text>As the satellite's FTL core is finishes charging it swings around its weapons cluster and fires a full barrage into itself. The resulting explosion is substantial and a plasma spike scorches your ship's hull.</text>
