	<text>Your ship is caught in the massive explosion that completely annihilates the satellite.</text>
	<text>As the satellite's overloaded FTL core ignites, it jumps into higher space, only to immediately reappear right behind your ship! You put full power to the engines but cannot evade the following explosion. Debris parts smash through your shields and damage the ship.</text>
